data.description: OPEN SUN 1-3! Welcome to this 4-bed, 3-bath, 2-car multi-level in the highly desirable Leawood West neighborhood! Great curb appeal situated on a spacious, .3-acre corner lot. Exterior has been recently painted, adding to the overall appeal. Inside you'll find an open layout, featuring a formal LR, DR, and updated kitchen with freshly painted cabinets and new countertops. Kitchen overlooks a spacious family room with cozy fireplace and provides access to the large, fully fenced yard. Convenient & functional guest bedroom and updated 3/4 bath/laundry room on the above grade lower level offering versatility. Upper level with generously sized bedrooms. The primary features 3/4 bath and plenty of closet space. Enjoy this unbeatable location just off the Pacific St corridor, providing quick and easy access to the Dodge Express & I80 and close proximity to great schools, parks, pool, restaurants, and shops.
